  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time multiplayer LAN gameplay with Socket.IO",
    "Strategic card combat system with type advantages",
    "Card fusion mechanics to create higher-level cards",
    "Six elemental card types: Fire, Water, Plant, Light, Shadow, Spirit",
    "Turn-based gameplay with 12-second turn timer",
    "User authentication and registration system"
